%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20got%20all%20these%20people%20sitting%20on%20retirement%20income%20who%20are%20losing%20money%20because%20of%20lower%20%E2%80%94%20as%20short%20rates%20come%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219484f46-664e-4c78-a4d8-b1aae2c928c1%5C%22%3EHesitant%20borrowers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20a%20suit%20next%20to%20a%20Wall%20Street%20sign%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68bef8bb57d362d375e7b80d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E60%25%20of%20firms%20that%20work%20with%20small%20businesses%20said%20that%20capital%20spending%20plans%20looked%20worse%20than%20they%20did%20six%20months%20ago.%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFed%20rate%20cuts%20are%20thought%20to%20rev%20up%20the%20economy%20by%20making%20capital%20cheaper%20for%20businesses%20and%20consumers.%20But%20the%20Fed%20jumpstarting%20its%20rate-cutting%20cycle%20might%20have%20the%20opposite%20effect%2C%20Kelly%20speculated%2C%20as%20borrowers%20will%20be%20incentivized%20to%20wait%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Finterest-rates%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einterest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20drop%20even%20more%20before%20taking%20out%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20tell%20people%20that%20more%20rate%20cuts%20%5Bare%5D%20coming.%20So%2C%20why%20borrow%20now%3F%20Let's%20wait%20and%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoan%20officers%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.federalreserve.gov%2Fdata%2Fsloos%2Fsloos-202507.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweaker%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20commercial%20and%20industrial%20loans%20for%20companies%20of%20all%20sizes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Fed's%20July%20Senior%20Loan%20Officer%20Opinion%20Survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E60%25%20of%